While travel plans remain up in the air, it's the perfect opportunity to catch up on all those travel books that are piling up next to the bed. At the link in bio, we've rounded up the top travel books to read in self-isolation, such as 'Eat Pray Love' by Elizabeth Gilbert, which showcases the beautiful wonders of India, Bali and Italy. ⠀
